    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Here's a great chance to own a solid, well-cared-for vehicle at a fair price! This car is in good condition \u2014 it runs reliably and handles beautifully, with only the minor cosmetic signs of everyday use you'd expect from a well-loved car. The interior is comfortable and functional, and the exterior presents nicely with just a few small scuffs that are totally typical for its age. If you're looking for a dependable, enjoyable daily driver without paying mint-condition prices, this one deserves a serious look!",
