    },
    {
      "id": "standard_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_2",
      "description": "This used car is in fair condition. The exterior has visible dents, scratches, and areas of faded or chipped paint on several panels. The interior shows noticeable wear including scuffed surfaces, some staining, and worn upholstery. The mechanical components are functional but may have some issues that should be addressed. Overall, this car is drivable but will require attention to bring it up to good condition.",
      "price": 20000.0,
