    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition, and we are genuinely excited to present what is truly an outstanding example. The exterior is immaculate \u2014 the paint retains a brilliant, deep shine with absolutely no scratches, chips, or blemishes of any kind. Every panel is straight and true, the glass is crystal clear, and the trim pieces are all intact and gleaming. Step inside and you'll find an interior that looks and smells as fresh as the day it left the showroom \u2014 the seats show no wear, the carpets are spotless, and every surface is pristine. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health: the engine runs smoothly and powerfully, all systems function exactly as intended, and there are no warning lights or known issues. This is the kind of vehicle that is increasingly rare to find, and it represents a genuine opportunity for a buyer who wants a car they can be proud of from day one.",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture before you decide. The exterior shows noticeable wear \u2014 you'll find scratches, some paint fade, and minor dents in a few areas. There is light surface rust in spots, though nothing structurally severe. The interior is functional but worn, with visible scuffs on the upholstery and some trim pieces showing their age. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some routine maintenance attention in the near term \u2014 think fluid changes, possibly new brake pads, and a general inspection. This is a practical, get-around vehicle for a buyer who doesn't mind cosmetic imperfections and wants reliable transportation without paying a premium price.",
      "price": 15500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Honest Deal & Ready to Roll \u2013 A Dependable Fair-Condition Value! \ud83d\ude97\n\nLooking for a practical vehicle that delivers solid everyday performance without the premium price tag? Look no further! We'll be completely transparent with you: this car is in fair condition, meaning it has seen some use and shows normal signs of wear \u2014 but it's mechanically functional and ready to serve you well on daily commutes and errands.\n\nExpect some cosmetic imperfections like minor scuffs or interior wear \u2014 nothing unusual for a car at this stage of its life. What you get is honest, straightforward transportation at a price that makes sense. No surprises, no hidden issues \u2014 just a reliable ride at a fair value. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself! \ud83d\ude4c",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Solid, dependable, and ready for the daily grind \u2014 a smart pick for the practical driver! This car is in fair condition, which means it's mechanically sound and will get you where you need to go without drama. You'll notice some cosmetic wear and minor imperfections that come with real-world use, but nothing that gets in the way of reliable everyday performance. If you're looking for honest transportation at an honest price, this one checks the box!",
      "price": 15500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a poor-condition car, best suited for buyers on a very tight budget, project vehicle enthusiasts, or anyone needing bare-bones point-A-to-point-B transportation. The exterior shows significant wear, including visible rust, dents, and faded or peeling paint in multiple areas \u2014 this is not a car that will turn heads for the right reasons. The interior is similarly worn, with torn or heavily stained upholstery, cracked trim pieces, and a dashboard that shows its age. Mechanically, the car runs but should be expected to need repairs, possibly including work on the engine, transmission, brakes, or suspension \u2014 a pre-purchase inspection by a trusted mechanic is strongly recommended before committing. Electrical components may be unreliable, and minor to moderate issues with lights, windows, or other accessories are possible. This vehicle is priced accordingly and represents an opportunity for someone willing to put in the time and money to bring it back to life, or simply someone who needs cheap, functional transportation in the short term. No warranties or guarantees are implied.",
      "price": 4750.0,
